Package medical

package medical
This package contains medical-related classes for the insurance system. It includes classes for medical records, healthcare providers, and visit types.

The classes in this package help manage medical data linked to patients.

  • Class
    Description
    Consultation
    Represents a medical consultation.
    ConsultationType
    Defines the type of consultation for an insurance claim.
    DiagnosticCode
    Represents a diagnostic code, typically used for medical diagnosis.
    EmergencyVisit
    Represents an emergency visit for a patient, which includes details about the accident type, police report number (if applicable), and the admission details.
    Medication
    Represents a medication with associated details loaded from a CSV file.
    MedicationBillableItem
    Represents a billable item for medication in an insurance claim.
    ProcedureCode
    Represents a medical procedure code with associated description and price.
    Visit
    Represents an inpatient hospital visit.
    VisitStatus
    Defines the status of a patient's visit.
    WardStay
    Represents a patient's stay in a hospital ward, including the ward information and the duration of the stay.
